Combine cereal crumbs and melted butter. Press in the bottom and up the sides of a 9 inch pie pan. Chill. Mix pudding according to directions on the package using 2 cups of milk. Blend in cream cheese. Fold in 1 cup whipped topping. Pour filling into crust. Chill 2 to 4 hours prior to serving. Garnish with remaining whipped topping and additional cereal pieces.